title: Ebro Darden Explains What Rappers Owe to the Culture & The Evolution of Hip Hop | ICONIC INTERVIEW
description:
Olayemi Olurin interviewed Hot 97's Ebro Darden about his 20 year career, how hip hop has evolved, his takes on the new artists like Chloe and Shenseea and some old artists who've surprised him like Lil Uzi Vert, and what artists like Drake owe to the Black community
